===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}} (''abbreviation'' '''[[DNA]]''')

# {{lb|en|genetics|biochemistry}} A [[nucleic acid]] found in all living things (and some non-living, see [[virus]]); consists of a [[polymer]] formed from [[nucleotide]]s which are [[shaped]] into a [[double]] [[helix]]; it is [[associated]] with the [[transmission]] of [[genetic]] [[information]].
#: {{syn|en|deoxyribose nucleic acid|desoxyribose nucleic acid|double helix}}
#: {{mer|en|nucleotide}}

